Shoprite Cleared by Zambia Competition Regulator, Reuters Says

-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 
2011-03-29T10:47:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/shoprite-cleared-by-zambia-competition-regulator-reuters-says.html
Shoprite Holdings Ltd. (SHP)  was cleared
by Zambia’s competition and consumer protection commission on
allegations that it abused its market power, Reuters reported,
citing the commission’s spokesman, Brian Lingela.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  